CREATE TABLE call_center (cc_call_center_sk INT, cc_call_center_id VARCHAR(1000), cc_rec_start_date DATE, cc_rec_end_date DATE, cc_closed_date_sk INT, cc_open_date_sk INT, cc_name VARCHAR(1000), cc_class VARCHAR(1000), cc_employees INT, cc_sq_ft INT, cc_hours VARCHAR(1000), cc_manager VARCHAR(1000), cc_mkt_id INT, cc_mkt_class VARCHAR(1000), cc_mkt_desc VARCHAR(1000), cc_market_manager VARCHAR(1000), cc_division INT, cc_division_name VARCHAR(1000), cc_company INT, cc_company_name VARCHAR(1000), cc_street_number VARCHAR(1000), cc_street_name VARCHAR(1000), cc_street_type VARCHAR(1000), cc_suite_number VARCHAR(1000), cc_city VARCHAR(1000), cc_county VARCHAR(1000), cc_state VARCHAR(1000), cc_zip VARCHAR(1000), cc_country VARCHAR(1000), cc_gmt_offset DECIMAL(5,2), cc_tax_percentage DECIMAL(5,2)) WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN, HEAP)
CREATE TABLE catalog_page (cp_catalog_page_sk INT, cp_catalog_page_id VARCHAR(1000), cp_start_date_sk INT, cp_end_date_sk INT, cp_department VARCHAR(1000), cp_catalog_number INT, cp_catalog_page_number INT, cp_description VARCHAR(1000), cp_type VARCHAR(1000)) 
CREATE TABLE catalog_returns (cr_returned_time_sk INT, cr_item_sk INT, cr_refunded_customer_sk INT, cr_refunded_cdemo_sk INT, cr_refunded_hdemo_sk INT, cr_refunded_addr_sk INT, cr_returning_customer_sk INT, cr_returning_cdemo_sk INT, cr_returning_hdemo_sk INT, cr_returning_addr_sk INT, cr_call_center_sk INT, cr_catalog_page_sk INT, cr_ship_mode_sk INT, cr_warehouse_sk INT, cr_reason_sk INT, cr_order_number BIGINT, cr_return_quantity INT, cr_return_amount DECIMAL(7,2), cr_return_tax DECIMAL(7,2), cr_return_amt_inc_tax DECIMAL(7,2), cr_fee DECIMAL(7,2), cr_return_ship_cost DECIMAL(7,2), cr_refunded_cash DECIMAL(7,2), cr_reversed_charge DECIMAL(7,2), cr_store_credit DECIMAL(7,2), cr_net_loss DECIMAL(7,2), cr_returned_date_sk VARCHAR(100)) WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN, HEAP)
CREATE TABLE catalog_sales (cs_sold_time_sk INT, cs_ship_date_sk INT, cs_bill_customer_sk INT, cs_bill_cdemo_sk INT, cs_bill_hdemo_sk INT, cs_bill_addr_sk INT, cs_ship_customer_sk INT, cs_ship_cdemo_sk INT, cs_ship_hdemo_sk INT, cs_ship_addr_sk INT, cs_call_center_sk INT, cs_catalog_page_sk INT, cs_ship_mode_sk INT, cs_warehouse_sk INT, cs_item_sk INT, cs_promo_sk INT, cs_order_number BIGINT, cs_quantity INT, cs_wholesale_cost DECIMAL(7,2), cs_list_price DECIMAL(7,2), cs_sales_price DECIMAL(7,2), cs_ext_discount_amt DECIMAL(7,2), cs_ext_sales_price DECIMAL(7,2), cs_ext_wholesale_cost DECIMAL(7,2), cs_ext_list_price DECIMAL(7,2), cs_ext_tax DECIMAL(7,2), cs_coupon_amt DECIMAL(7,2), cs_ext_ship_cost DECIMAL(7,2), cs_net_paid DECIMAL(7,2), cs_net_paid_inc_tax DECIMAL(7,2), cs_net_paid_inc_ship DECIMAL(7,2), cs_net_paid_inc_ship_tax DECIMAL(7,2), cs_net_profit DECIMAL(7,2), cs_sold_date_sk VARCHAR(100)) WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN, HEAP)
CREATE TABLE customer (c_customer_sk INT, c_customer_id VARCHAR(1000), c_current_cdemo_sk INT, c_current_hdemo_sk INT, c_current_addr_sk  INT, c_first_shipto_date_sk INT, c_first_sales_date_sk INT, c_salutation VARCHAR(1000), c_first_name VARCHAR(1000), c_last_name VARCHAR(1000), c_preferred_cust_flag VARCHAR(1000), c_birth_day INT, c_birth_month INT, c_birth_year INT, c_birth_country VARCHAR(1000), c_login VARCHAR(1000), c_email_address VARCHAR(1000), c_last_review_date VARCHAR(1000)) WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN, HEAP)  
CREATE TABLE customer_address (ca_address_sk INT, ca_address_id VARCHAR(1000), ca_street_number VARCHAR(1000), ca_street_name VARCHAR(1000), ca_street_type VARCHAR(1000), ca_suite_number VARCHAR(1000), ca_city VARCHAR(1000), ca_county VARCHAR(1000), ca_state VARCHAR(1000), ca_zip VARCHAR(1000), ca_country VARCHAR(1000), ca_gmt_offset DECIMAL(5,2), ca_location_type VARCHAR(1000)) WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN, HEAP)  
CREATE TABLE customer_demographics (cd_demo_sk INT, cd_gender VARCHAR(1000), cd_marital_status VARCHAR(1000), cd_education_status VARCHAR(1000), cd_purchase_estimate INT, cd_credit_rating VARCHAR(1000), cd_dep_count INT, cd_dep_employed_count INT, cd_dep_college_count INT);
CREATE TABLE date_dim (d_date_sk INT, d_date_id VARCHAR(1000), d_date DATE, d_month_seq INT, d_week_seq INT, d_quarter_seq INT, d_year INT, d_dow INT, d_moy INT, d_dom INT, d_qoy INT, d_fy_year INT, d_fy_quarter_seq INT, d_fy_week_seq INT, d_day_name VARCHAR(1000), d_quarter_name VARCHAR(1000), d_holiday VARCHAR(1000), d_weekend VARCHAR(1000), d_following_holiday VARCHAR(1000), d_first_dom INT, d_last_dom INT, d_same_day_ly INT, d_same_day_lq INT, d_current_day VARCHAR(1000), d_current_week VARCHAR(1000), d_current_month VARCHAR(1000), d_current_quarter VARCHAR(1000), d_current_year VARCHAR(1000)) WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN, HEAP)
CREATE TABLE household_demographics (hd_demo_sk INT, hd_income_band_sk INT, hd_buy_potential VARCHAR(1000), hd_dep_count INT, hd_vehicle_count INT);
CREATE TABLE income_band (ib_income_band_sk INT, ib_lower_bound INT, ib_upper_bound INT);
CREATE TABLE inventory (inv_item_sk INT, inv_warehouse_sk INT, inv_quantity_on_hand INT, inv_date_sk VARCHAR(100)) WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN, HEAP)
CREATE TABLE item (i_item_sk INT, i_item_id VARCHAR(1000), i_rec_start_date DATE, i_rec_end_date DATE, i_item_desc VARCHAR(1000), i_current_price DECIMAL(7,2), i_wholesale_cost DECIMAL(7,2), i_brand_id INT, i_brand VARCHAR(1000), i_class_id INT, i_class VARCHAR(1000), i_category_id INT, i_category VARCHAR(1000), i_manufact_id INT, i_manufact VARCHAR(1000), i_size VARCHAR(1000), i_formulation VARCHAR(1000), i_color VARCHAR(1000), i_units VARCHAR(1000), i_container VARCHAR(1000), i_manager_id INT, i_product_name VARCHAR(1000)) WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN, HEAP)
CREATE TABLE promotion (p_promo_sk INT, p_promo_id VARCHAR(1000), p_start_date_sk INT, p_end_date_sk INT, p_item_sk INT, p_cost DECIMAL(15,2), p_response_target INT, p_promo_name VARCHAR(1000), p_channel_dmail VARCHAR(1000), p_channel_email VARCHAR(1000), p_channel_catalog VARCHAR(1000), p_channel_tv VARCHAR(1000), p_channel_radio VARCHAR(1000), p_channel_press VARCHAR(1000), p_channel_event VARCHAR(1000), p_channel_demo VARCHAR(1000), p_channel_details VARCHAR(1000), p_purpose VARCHAR(1000), p_discount_active VARCHAR(1000)) WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN, HEAP)
CREATE TABLE reason (r_reason_sk INT, r_reason_id VARCHAR(1000), r_reason_desc VARCHAR(1000)) WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN, HEAP)
CREATE TABLE ship_mode (sm_ship_mode_sk INT, sm_ship_mode_id VARCHAR(1000), sm_type VARCHAR(1000), sm_code VARCHAR(1000), sm_carrier VARCHAR(1000), sm_contract VARCHAR(1000)) WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN, HEAP)  
CREATE TABLE store (s_store_sk INT, s_store_id VARCHAR(1000), s_rec_start_date DATE, s_rec_end_date DATE, s_closed_date_sk INT, s_store_name VARCHAR(1000), s_number_employees INT, s_floor_space INT, s_hours VARCHAR(1000), s_manager VARCHAR(1000), s_market_id INT, s_geography_class VARCHAR(1000), s_market_desc VARCHAR(1000), s_market_manager VARCHAR(1000), s_division_id INT, s_division_name VARCHAR(1000), s_company_id INT, s_company_name VARCHAR(1000), s_street_number VARCHAR(1000), s_street_name VARCHAR(1000), s_street_type VARCHAR(1000), s_suite_number VARCHAR(1000), s_city VARCHAR(1000), s_county VARCHAR(1000), s_state VARCHAR(1000), s_zip VARCHAR(1000), s_country VARCHAR(1000), s_gmt_offset DECIMAL(5,2), s_tax_precentage DECIMAL(5,2)) WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN, HEAP)
CREATE TABLE store_returns (sr_return_time_sk INT, sr_item_sk INT, sr_customer_sk INT, sr_cdemo_sk INT, sr_hdemo_sk INT, sr_addr_sk INT, sr_store_sk INT, sr_reason_sk INT, sr_ticket_number BIGINT, sr_return_quantity INT, sr_return_amt DECIMAL(7,2), sr_return_tax DECIMAL(7,2), sr_return_amt_inc_tax DECIMAL(7,2), sr_fee DECIMAL(7,2), sr_return_ship_cost DECIMAL(7,2), sr_refunded_cash DECIMAL(7,2), sr_reversed_charge DECIMAL(7,2), sr_store_credit DECIMAL(7,2), sr_net_loss DECIMAL(7,2), sr_returned_date_sk VARCHAR(100)) WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN, HEAP)  
CREATE TABLE store_sales (ss_sold_time_sk INT, ss_item_sk INT, ss_customer_sk INT, ss_cdemo_sk INT, ss_hdemo_sk INT, ss_addr_sk INT, ss_store_sk INT, ss_promo_sk INT, ss_ticket_number BIGINT, ss_quantity INT, ss_wholesale_cost DECIMAL(7,2), ss_list_price DECIMAL(7,2), ss_sales_price DECIMAL(7,2), ss_ext_discount_amt DECIMAL(7,2), ss_ext_sales_price DECIMAL(7,2), ss_ext_wholesale_cost DECIMAL(7,2), ss_ext_list_price DECIMAL(7,2), ss_ext_tax DECIMAL(7,2), ss_coupon_amt DECIMAL(7,2), ss_net_paid DECIMAL(7,2), ss_net_paid_inc_tax DECIMAL(7,2), ss_net_profit DECIMAL(7,2), ss_sold_date_sk VARCHAR(100)) WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN, HEAP)
CREATE TABLE time_dim (t_time_sk INT, t_time_id VARCHAR(1000), t_time INT, t_hour INT, t_minute INT, t_second INT, t_am_pm VARCHAR(1000), t_shift VARCHAR(1000), t_sub_shift VARCHAR(1000), t_meal_time VARCHAR(1000)) WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN, HEAP)
CREATE TABLE warehouse (w_warehouse_sk INT, w_warehouse_id VARCHAR(1000), w_warehouse_name VARCHAR(1000), w_warehouse_sq_ft INT, w_street_number VARCHAR(1000), w_street_name VARCHAR(1000), w_street_type VARCHAR(1000), w_suite_number VARCHAR(1000), w_city VARCHAR(1000), w_county VARCHAR(1000), w_state VARCHAR(1000), w_zip VARCHAR(1000), w_country VARCHAR(1000), w_gmt_offset DECIMAL(5,2)) WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN, HEAP)  
CREATE TABLE web_page (wp_web_page_sk INT, wp_web_page_id VARCHAR(1000), wp_rec_start_date DATE, wp_rec_end_date DATE, wp_creation_date_sk INT, wp_access_date_sk INT, wp_autogen_flag VARCHAR(1000), wp_customer_sk INT, wp_url VARCHAR(1000), wp_type VARCHAR(1000), wp_char_count INT, wp_link_count INT, wp_image_count INT, wp_max_ad_count INT);
CREATE TABLE web_returns (wr_returned_time_sk INT, wr_item_sk INT, wr_refunded_customer_sk INT, wr_refunded_cdemo_sk INT, wr_refunded_hdemo_sk INT, wr_refunded_addr_sk INT, wr_returning_customer_sk INT, wr_returning_cdemo_sk INT, wr_returning_hdemo_sk INT, wr_returning_addr_sk INT, wr_web_page_sk INT, wr_reason_sk INT, wr_order_number BIGINT, wr_return_quantity INT, wr_return_amt DECIMAL(7,2), wr_return_tax DECIMAL(7,2), wr_return_amt_inc_tax DECIMAL(7,2), wr_fee DECIMAL(7,2), wr_return_ship_cost DECIMAL(7,2), wr_refunded_cash DECIMAL(7,2), wr_reversed_charge DECIMAL(7,2), wr_account_credit DECIMAL(7,2), wr_net_loss DECIMAL(7,2), wr_returned_date_sk VARCHAR(100)) WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN, HEAP)
CREATE TABLE web_sales (ws_sold_time_sk INT, ws_ship_date_sk INT, ws_item_sk INT, ws_bill_customer_sk INT, ws_bill_cdemo_sk INT,  ws_bill_hdemo_sk INT, ws_bill_addr_sk INT, ws_ship_customer_sk INT, ws_ship_cdemo_sk INT, ws_ship_hdemo_sk INT, ws_ship_addr_sk INT, ws_web_page_sk INT, ws_web_site_sk INT, ws_ship_mode_sk INT, ws_warehouse_sk INT, ws_promo_sk INT, ws_order_number BIGINT, ws_quantity INT, ws_wholesale_cost DECIMAL(7,2), ws_list_price DECIMAL(7,2), ws_sales_price DECIMAL(7,2), ws_ext_discount_amt DECIMAL(7,2), ws_ext_sales_price DECIMAL(7,2), ws_ext_wholesale_cost DECIMAL(7,2), ws_ext_list_price DECIMAL(7,2), ws_ext_tax DECIMAL(7,2), ws_coupon_amt DECIMAL(7,2), ws_ext_ship_cost DECIMAL(7,2), ws_net_paid DECIMAL(7,2), ws_net_paid_inc_tax DECIMAL(7,2), ws_net_paid_inc_ship DECIMAL(7,2), ws_net_paid_inc_ship_tax DECIMAL(7,2), ws_net_profit DECIMAL(7,2), ws_sold_date_sk VARCHAR(100)) WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN, HEAP)  
CREATE TABLE web_site (web_site_sk INT, web_site_id VARCHAR(1000), web_rec_start_date DATE, web_rec_end_date DATE, web_name VARCHAR(1000), web_open_date_sk INT, web_close_date_sk INT, web_class VARCHAR(1000), web_manager VARCHAR(1000), web_mkt_id INT, web_mkt_class VARCHAR(1000), web_mkt_desc VARCHAR(1000), web_market_manager VARCHAR(1000), web_company_id INT, web_company_name VARCHAR(1000), web_street_number VARCHAR(1000), web_street_name VARCHAR(1000),  web_street_type VARCHAR(1000), web_suite_number VARCHAR(1000), web_city VARCHAR(1000), web_county VARCHAR(1000), web_state VARCHAR(1000), web_zip VARCHAR(1000), web_country VARCHAR(1000), web_gmt_offset DECIMAL(5,2), web_tax_percentage DECIMAL(5,2)) WITH (DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN, HEAP) 
GO
